        "created_at": "2020-08-04T19:48:36.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Here\u2019s another video from Burgundy, this time Domaine Leflaive\u2019s Clavoillon, taken today. Looks like there\u2019s a bit of \u201cmillerandange\u201d, and it seems that Leflaive has also performed a green harvest as you can see the desiccating discarded clusters on the ground.</p>\n<div class=\"youtube-onebox lazy-video-container\" data-video-id=\"VXQ3VZOI0x8\" data-video-title=\"Domaine Leflaive's Puligny-Montrachet 1er Cru Clavoillon in early August 2020\" data-video-start-time=\"\" data-provider-name=\"youtube\">\n  <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VXQ3VZOI0x8\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">\n    <img class=\"youtube-thumbnail\" src=\"https://www.wineberserkers.com/uploads/db0731/original/3X/4/c/4cd4d465e03126ea02e400442cd49b2c2085b94d.jpeg\" title=\"Domaine Leflaive's Puligny-Montrachet 1er Cru Clavoillon in early August 2020\" data-dominant-color=\"4C4139\" width=\"480\" height=\"360\">\n  </a>\n</div>\n",
